  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nHard fork 1 adds two fields to the `BeaconState` (`current_epoch_participation`, `previous_epoch_participation`) with `List[Bitvector]` type (Teku type `SSZList<SSZVector<BitView>>`). The list length would be the same as `validators` \r\n\r\nNeed to make sure this works and works with acceptable speed. \r\n\r\nProbably we would need to make a specific type for this (see #3540)",
